{"tid":582867,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"調查指 iPhone X、iPhone 8 機價太貴　用戶不想升級","createTime":"2018-03-06T13:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T09:34:43.000Z","uid":64694,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"876b9d7aa61b8bdc0b863b2a09154388aca12a3c","tid":582867,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:49:07.000Z","msg":"去年蘋果推出 iPhone X、iPhone 8 與 8 Plus 三款新機。但有一個調查發現，有 3 個主要因素令現有 iPhone 用戶打消升級電話的念頭。分別是現有 iPhone 仍運作良好、新 iPhone 定價過高、以及認為 iPhone X 的熒幕太細。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據 Barron&rsquo;s 週刊報道，調查由投資銀行 Piper Jaffray 進行，囊括 1,500 購買最新一代 iPhone 的受訪者，當中 44% 的人沒有升級電話的主要原因是現有 iPhone 仍運作良好。而當中 31% 受訪者是因為新 iPhone 定價過高。同時亦有 8% 人指，希望 iPhone X 熒幕太細，希望蘋果推出更大熒幕版本。另外有 17% 受訪者因其他原因而拒絕升級。<br />\n<br />\nPiper Jaffray 指，蘋果在年內推出的新產品，將能滿足因為不滿售價及熒幕尺寸而拒絕升級的用家。他們預計，蘋果將於年內推出 3 部新 iPhone ，當中包括採用 6.5 吋熒幕的 iPhone X Plus ，以及搭載 LCD 熒幕及定價較具競爭力的 6.1 吋型號。雖然上述調查僅訪問 1,500 人，無法忠實呈現整體市場實況，但仍能讓蘋果得知新旗艦無法吸引部分用家的原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/03/06/reason-of-refusing-upgrade-iphone/mobile-phone/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2Freason-of-refusing-upgrade-iphone%2Fmobile-phone%2Famp%2F&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=bda97640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/03/06/reason-of-refusing-upgrade-iphone/mobile-phone/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果之後新出嘅iPhone X減價，而家買咗iPhone X班人真係做白老鼠，重要蝕埋錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc6725d133dbd9b53de927a5e557dfc2ca63433","tid":582867,"uid":26451,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:50:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"123c0a56930890687dcc1d42404c54e4c0da6948","tid":582867,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:52:27.000Z","msg":"